{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"e4ca4d09-185c-4039-8b7b-75041d97e51a","content":"I should clarify: **CLR activation logs** diagnose issues with loading/selecting the .NET runtime (e.g., wrong version picked, runtime not found). A **NullReferenceException** is a runtime bug in your application code — it means you're accessing a member on a `null` reference.\n\nThese are two different problems:\n\n- **CLR activation logs** → \"which runtime loaded?\" issues\n- **NullReferenceException** → a bug in your code (null variable, uninitialized object, etc.)\n\nTo help you, I need to know which issue you're facing:\n\n1. **If the app fails to start at all** (wrong runtime, missing runtime), I can invoke the CLR activation debugging skill to analyze activation logs.\n2. **If the app starts but then crashes with a NullReferenceException**, you need to look at the stack trace of the exception to find the null reference. Can you share the exception stack trace or relevant code?\n\nWhich is it, or would you like help with both?","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"97ace89a-124e-4957-9954-276cb8f50dbb","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user is asking me to analyze CLR activation logs to diagnose a NullReferenceException in their .NET app. However, I don't see any files in the working directory yet, and a NullReferenceException is typically a runtime error, not a CLR activation issue.\n\nLet me first check if there are any files in the working directory, and also consider whether the CLR activation debugging skill is relevant here.\n\nActually, the user specifically mentioned \"CLR activation logs\" - let me check if there are any log files available. But also, a NullReferenceException is not typically a CLR activation issue. CLR activation is about loading the correct .NET runtime version. A NullReferenceException is a runtime bug in application code.\n\n\nI should start by checking what files are available in the working directory to see if there are any logs or diagnostic information I can work with.","outputTokens":428,"requestId":"CAE7:25F786:1E9CD5E:21C7FD3:6A0526AC"},"id":"c43be6b0-28e4-4f90-87bd-c767dd5d8b50","timestamp":"2026-05-14T01:34:47.586Z","parentId":"e16f1e16-609e-4966-a47b-c9a1d5f06fab"}
